collaborators.name: Ava Jones
collaborators.about: My art background is in photography and studio art. I mostly work with acrylic paint right now, but have been experimenting with painting found objects and assembling them together as a kind of sculpture.

collaborators.name: Bruno Garcia
collaborators.about: I am a self-taught painter. I enjoy bright colors and mostly abstract work. I am not a working artist, but paint more to relax and meet new people.

collaborators.name: Lily Potter
collaborators.about: Hi! I'm Lily, and I am just starting my art degree. I have always loved to draw, but hope to expand my knowledge into watercolor and other painting mediums.

collaborators.name: Tamika Roberts
collaborators.about: Hello, my name is Tamika, and I am a children's book illustrator. I love to spend time with other artists, and I am looking for a collaborator to help me illustrate my next book project.

collaborators.name: Jackson Townsend
collaborators.about: My main work is comic book art. Mostly graphic novels, but I also do some editorial. My favorite thing to work with is paper collage and ink.

labs.name: Paint It, Black?
labs.about: An exercise in minimalism, this LAB will experiment with the use of only black paint, ink and charcoals.

labs.name: Drink and Draw
labs.about: BYODrink of choice, and join us for a laid back drawing session.

labs.name: While My MacBook Gently Weeps
labs.about: New to world of digital arts, and feeling weepy? Come together, right now, in this Beatles themed LAB, to HELP! each other learn.
